items.text: Eggs Royale.
Awesome peanut butter cookies and a really awesome ambience.
The serving for eggs benedict was small ($14) and eggs could be runnier. Truffle fries were good though.
Food is decent, drinks better than most. Had the Riesling tea & mocha. Wifi password is pasted on the till at the order counter.
Truffle fries were great as what everyone else said. The eggs on the bendicts were undercooked and the baked eggs didnt taste as good as it looked.
Please be considerate to announce on Facebook or your own website that you're NOT opened on Good Friday, and not simply leave a note on the door! Wasted trip.

The coffee is really not bad! Truffle fries were alright.
Truffle fries were reallllllly good! Eggs bennies and French toast were average. Side of fruits on the french toast was too sour.
Nice environment for a Friday lunch. Menu was limited. Bangers & mash were ordinary.
Very nice place. Breakfast is OK.
Truffle fries are really good!!!
Slow service but friendly team.
Coffee isn't that great but what's worse was the rum crepe cake. Avoid!
Best truffle fries! MUST TRY!
Must try! Bread pudding with Vanilla sauce S$6
Nicest service staff ever. Though they ran out of mains, the chef offered to cook us off-menu items and came out to make apologies. Kudos!

Curly fries! Fries! Bread and butter pudding. Will try chicken wings next.
Great coffee, enjoyed my skinny flat white...
Unfortunately don't see the big deal with the food. Just usual fare.  Coffee good though.
They've improved since I last reviewed them. I recommend the all day breakfast: Eggs Royale. Full marks for presentation! Coffee is good, too.
Very well done and executed. Lots of fried stuff on the menu...but who doesn't like fried?!?
Nothing special about the place. Very average food which is still better than the service.
Best truffle fries in Singapore, in my opinion. Pricing is good too! Excellent for cafehopping OLs.
Best truffles fries.
simple settings with surprisingly good food! and cookies! lots of amazing cookies

never leave without a hummingbird cake
Nice place within Cbd serving all day breakfast and a separate daily menu. Nice!!

the egg bendict is niceeee~

Truffle fries!

Picked their recommended Shrimp Paste Chicken Wrap from the Friday lunch menu. Loved it! Tasty chicken pieces paired elegantly with their creamy Sriracha (hot Thai sauce) mayo. I'd order this again
Best burgers in telok ayer street #portobello
Loving the homemade granola with fresh fruits and yogurt!!

Bright, cosy atmosphere, friendly service and great food. Brunch on a sat. here is recommended!
Nice relaxt atmosphere and nice food

Mixed mushroom and tomato pasta was so flavorful and delicious! Best pasta of the month!
Excellent warm bread pudding (croissant? Pain au chocolat? Nutella?), topped with sugar crystals, served with chilled creme Anglaise.
